# ========================================
# SECURITY-FOCUSED .gitignore
# Updated: January 1, 2026
# Lesson learned: Never commit credentials!
# ========================================

# === CRITICAL: SPECIFIC FILES FROM SECURITY INCIDENT ===
# These files contained credentials - NEVER commit them
Claude/CLAUDE.md
Claude/MFA_Configuration/*token*.txt
Claude/Anti-Malware/*API*
Claude/Anti-Malware/Virus*Total*
Certification and Compliance Evidence/back-up*Key*
Certification and Compliance Evidence/backup*key*
Updated_Passwords.md
**/Updated_Passwords.md

# === CREDENTIALS & SECRETS (PATTERNS) ===
# Block ALL extensions, not just .txt (lesson learned 2026-02-04)
*password*
*Password*
*PASSWORD*
*credential*
*Credential*
*secret*
*Secret*
*token*
*Token*
*api*key*
*apikey*
*API*KEY*
*creds*
*Creds*

# Actual key files
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx

# Environment files
.env
.env.*
*.env

# Configuration files with credentials
*credentials.txt
*creds.txt
wazuh-credentials*
roundcube*password*
.smbcredentials
.git-credentials

# === SSL/TLS CERTIFICATES ===
# Keep documentation, exclude actual certs
*.crt
*.cer
*.csr
!**/SSL_Certificate_Reference/*.md
!**/SSL_Certificate_Reference/*.txt

# === BACKUP FILES ===
*.backup
*.bak
*~
*.swp
*.swo

# === TEMPORARY FILES ===
*.tmp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# === LOG FILES ===
*.log

# === COMPILED FILES ===
*.pyc
*.pyo
__pycache__/

# === ARCHIVES ===
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.tgz

# === OFFICE TEMPORARY FILES ===
~$*

# === SENSITIVE DIRECTORIES ===
.ssh/
.gnupg/
**/private/
secrets/
.secrets/

# === ALLOW DOCUMENTATION (BUT NOT IF IT CONTAINS SECRETS) ===
# IMPORTANT: .md files CAN contain secrets (as we learned!)
# Only allow specific safe documentation files
!README.md
!TABLE_OF_CONTENTS.md
!RELEASE_NOTES*.md
!**/Chapter*.md
!**/Appendix*.md
# DO NOT use blanket !*.md - it overrides security patterns!

# ========================================
# PRE-COMMIT CHECKLIST:
# 1. Run: git status
# 2. Run: git diff --cached
# 3. Verify NO passwords/secrets in changes
# 4. When in doubt, DON'T commit!
# ========================================
